text: A motorcyclist killed in a crash in Florida in 2020 was listed as a COVID-19 death.
More people died of suicide in 2020 than died of COVID-19.
An image shared on Instagram claims about 489,000 people died from COVID-19 in 2020 compared to 650,000 from the seasonal flu in 2018 and 50 million from the Spanish flu in 1918.
